headline: BXP Releases 2024 Sustainability & Impact Report
summary: BOSTON, April 22, 2025--BXP (NYSE: BXP), the largest publicly traded developer, owner, and manager of premier workplaces in the United States, today announced the release of BXP’s 2024 Sustainability & Impact Report.
